  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the chopped bell pepper and cook until tender, about 5 minutes",
    "Add the cheonggukjang, smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine",
    "Add the basmati rice and stir to combine with the cheonggukjang mixture",
    "Add the lemon juice and stir to combine",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes",
    "Fluff the pilaf with a fork and stir in the chopped fresh parsley",
    "Serve the pilaf hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired"
